WEBVTT

01:43:29.921 --> 01:43:32.289
<i>Even when He seemed</i>
<i>indifferent to my</i>
<i>suffering...</i>

01:43:32.291 --> 01:43:34.557
<i>He was watching.</i>

01:43:34.559 --> 01:43:38.128
<i>And when I was</i>
<i>beyond all hope of savin,</i>
<i>He gave me rest...</i>

01:43:38.130 --> 01:43:40.897
<i>then gave me a sign</i>
<i>to continue my journey.</i>
